Package entity

Class Officer

java.lang.Object
entity.UserAccount
entity.Applicant
entity.Officer
public class Officer extends Applicant
The Officer class extends the Applicant class and represents an officer who manages projects. The officer can register to handle a project, view and reply to project enquiries, manage flat bookings, and generate reports related to the project they are assigned to. The officer's role behavior is determined using the RoleBehavior interface and OfficerBehavior class.
